<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OMNI // HYRED FORENSIC RECRUITER</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --surface: #101112;
            --surface-low: #18191a;
            --surface-high: #242526;
            --primary: #faf8ff;
            --cyber-green: #00FF41;
            --electric-blue: #d6dbff;
            --outline: #3b4b37;
            --font-main: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-radius: 0 !important;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--surface);
            color: var(--primary);
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--outline);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: var(--surface-low);
        }

        .system-id {
            color: var(--cyber-green);
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        main {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 400px 1fr;
            flex-grow: 1;
            gap: 1px;
            background: var(--outline);
        }

        .sidebar {
            background: var(--surface-low);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            overflow-y: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .canvas {
            background: var(--surface);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .module {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--outline);
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .module-header {
            background: var(--surface-high);
            margin: -1rem -1rem 1rem -1rem;
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            color: var(--cyber-green);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--outline);
        }

        .upload-zone {
            height: 150px;
            border: 2px dashed var(--outline);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .upload-zone:hover {
            border-color: var(--cyber-green);
            background: rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.05);
        }

        .btn-tactical {
            background: var(--surface-high);
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid var(--outline);
            padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .btn-tactical:hover {
            background: var(--cyber-green);
            color: var(--surface);
        }

        .analysis-card {
            background: var(--surface-low);
            border-left: 3px solid var(--electric-blue);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .score-pill {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--cyber-green);
            color: var(--surface);
            padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-left: 1rem;
        }

        #resume-preview {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            background: #000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #444;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--outline);
        }

        .field-group {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .field-label {
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            color: #888;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }

        .field-value {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            padding: 0.5rem;
            background: var(--surface-high);
            border: 1px solid var(--outline);
        }
    </style>
  <script type="module" src="/inject-aesthetic-global.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div>
            <div class="system-id">OMNI_NODE // HYRED_RECRUITER.v2.0</div>
            <div class="title">RECRUITMENT FORENSICS</div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn-tactical" style="width: auto;">EXPORT_PDF_REPORT</button>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="sidebar">
            <div class="module">
                <div class="module-header">ARTIFACT_INPUT</div>
                <div class="upload-zone" id="upload-zone">
                    <span style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">📁</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #888;">LOAD_RESUME_PDF_OR_IMAGE</span>
                </div>
                <input type="file" id="resume-input" style="display: none">
            </div>

            <div class="module">
                <div class="module-header">EXTRACTION_PARAMETERS</div>
                <div class="field-group">
                    <div class="field-label">PARSING_MODEL</div>
                    <div class="field-value">moondream:latest (Vision)</div>
                </div>
                <div class="field-group">
                    <div class="field-label">REWRITE_ENGINE</div>
                    <div class="field-value">llama3.2:3b (Text)</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="module">
                <div class="module-header">PREVIEW_WINDOW</div>
                <div id="resume-preview">NO_DOCUMENT_LOADED</div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="canvas">
            <div id="results-container">
                <div class="analysis-card" style="opacity: 0.5;">
                    <div style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Candidate Analysis Protocol V2.1</div>
                    <p>Awaiting artifact ingestion for forensic evaluation of skills, experience, and role alignment...</p>
                </div>

                <div class="module">
                    <div class="module-header">SKILL_MATRIX_PROJECTION</div>
                    <div style="height: 200px; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 10px; padding: 10px;">
                        <div style="background: var(--outline); width: 30px; height: 10%;"></div>
                        <div style="background: var(--outline); width: 30px; height: 10%;"></div>
                        <div style="background: var(--outline); width: 30px; height: 10%;"></div>
                        <div style="background: var(--outline); width: 30px; height: 10%;"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <script>
        const uploadZone = document.getElementById('upload-zone');
        const fileInput = document.getElementById('resume-input');
        const container = document.getElementById('results-container');

        uploadZone.onclick = () => fileInput.click();

        fileInput.onchange = async (e) => {
            const file = e.target.files[0];
            if (!file) return;

            document.getElementById('resume-preview').textContent = file.name;
            
            // Mock processing
            container.innerHTML = `
                <div class="analysis-card">
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        <div style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700;">${file.name.split('.')[0].toUpperCase()}</div>
                        <div class="score-pill">MATCH_INDEX: 92/100</div>
                    </div>
                    <strong>EXECUTIVE SUMMARY:</strong><br>
                    Candidate demonstrates exceptional proficiency in systems architecture and forensic data analysis. Previous tenure at Bit & Mortar indicates strong alignment with OMNI-CORE protocols. 
                    <br><br>
                    <strong>KEY STRENGTHS:</strong>
                    <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                        <li>Distributed Systems Design (High Density)</li>
                        <li>Vector Database Integration (Cerberus Expert)</li>
                        <li>Industrial Aesthetic Implementation</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="module">
                    <div class="module-header">OPTIMIZED_REWRITE_OUTPUT</div>
                    <div style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; background: var(--surface-low); padding: 1rem;">
                        [SKILLS UPDATE_SUCCESS]<br>
                        - Refactored "Proficient in Python" -> "Advanced Implementation of Distributed Python Microservices"<br>
                        - Enhanced "Built UI" -> "Architected High-Density Forensic Component Systems"
                    </div>
                </div>
            `;
        };
    </script>
</body>
</html>
